    "div" : "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-condition-ver-status.html\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/condition-ver-status</code></a><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFproblemVerificationStatus.html\">VF_problemVerificationStatus</a></b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-condition-ver-status.html#condition-ver-status-refuted\">refuted</a></td><td>refuted</td><td>This condition has been ruled out by subsequent diagnostic and clinical evidence.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-condition-ver-status.html#condition-ver-status-confirmed\">confirmed</a></td><td>confirmed</td><td>There is sufficient evidence to assert the presence of the subject's condition.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-condition-ver-status.html#condition-ver-status-provisional\">provisional</a></td><td>provisional</td><td>This is a tentative diagnosis - still a candidate that is under consideration.</td><td/></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <code>http://va.gov/terminology/vistaDefinedTerms/9000011-1.02</code><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFproblemVerificationStatus.html\">VF_problemVerificationStatus</a></b></td></tr><tr><td>H</td><td>HIDDEN</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-condition-ver-status.html#condition-ver-status-refuted\">refuted</a></td></tr><tr><td>P</td><td>PERMANENT</td><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-condition-ver-status.ht